260
0:10:45.26,000 --> 0:10:48,000
"Well, this thing came out ..." And I said, "Stop! Stop! Stop!

261
0:10:48.26,000 --> 0:10:51,000
I see; it's an island."

262
0:10:51.26,000 --> 0:10:53,000
And amazing.

263
0:10:53.26,000 --> 0:10:55,000
So Brownian motion, which happens to have

264
0:10:55.26,000 --> 0:10:58,000
