265
0:10:58.26,000 --> 0:11:,000
I measured it, 1.33.

266
0:11:00.26,000 --> 0:11:02,000
Again, again, again.

267
0:11:02.26,000 --> 0:11:04,000
Long measurements, big Brownian motions,

268
