0:12:39.26,000 --> 0:12:41,000
because they could do it much, much easier.

307
0:12:41.26,000 --> 0:12:44,000
But I tell you, at this point, people listened to me.

308
0:12:44.26,000 --> 0:12:46,000
(Laughter)

